snippet.title: Mars Underground Trailer #1: Meet Mars
snippet.description:
Currently on Kickstarter!  http://kck.st/2f4QK9g﻿

Meet Mars. 
Mars has just moved to a new city with his family. It's his first day at a new school.
Except every day is his first day at a new school.
Every morning Mars wakes up and relives the same day over and over again.
And then every night the world ends.

Play the demo:
MarsUnderground.net
